ends in charge transfer and doping observed in the XPS and PL results, where\nmetals such as Ni led to an n-type of doping, while Cu functionalization\nresults in p-type doping. Therefore, the formation of coordination complexes on\nTMD's surface is demonstrated to be a promising and effective way to control\nand to understand the nature of the single-atom functionalization of TMD.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Sep 2021 19:35:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-21"}
