 confirm the efficacy of the proposed scheme, where\nthe gain is particularly pronounced when the network grows in size because our\nmethod is able to adapt the channel access probabilities with the change of\nambient environment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 18 Sep 2021 03:54:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-21"}
